Sum of Even Numbers till N
Send Feedback
Given a number N, print sum of all even numbers from 1 to N.
Input Format :
Integer N
Output Format :
Required Sum 
Sample Input 1 :
 6
Sample Output 1 :
12

solution:


#include<iostream>
using namespace std;


int main(){
    int sum=0;
    int i=1;
    int n;
    cin>>n;
    while(i<=n){
        if(i%2==0){
            sum=sum+i;
        }
        i++;
    }
    cout<<sum;

       	/*  
		Read input as specified in the question.
		Print output as specified in the question.
	*/
  
}
